2. Second thing, have confidence in the power of you brain. We can collect limitless quantity of information and also recall it when needed, within the miracle called our brain. Now this can happen, only if we create a habit of collecting, retaining and recalling this information. So spend some time engaging in that habit. Its important because last second preparation will not help.

3. Third vital thing, practice, practice and much more practice. Try as numerous prep questions as possible find. The more the greater, spend time to choose questions which are on GAMSAT standards. This is actually the closest you can get to the GAMSAT because it doesn't have a official syllabus.

4. Dedication and determination is an essential key apart from all the preparation that goes into appearing for GAMSAT. After you have decided to take the exam, don't let anything else stop you from passing on your best shot. Remember it is simply an evaluation, but like everything else it requires focus.

5. GAMSAT is made to make students approach study systematically. This means to show and evaluate yourself. It requires you to identify your strengths and weakness and work at improving them. It also requires you to definitely understand your performance and close loops in the process of studying. In short learn from you mistakes and do not repeat them.

6. Take a look at managing your time and effort. This is a very important factor while appearing for that test. Since each question and section is timed the preparation has to be completed in an identical manner. So when you studying to gain knowledge practice time management as well.

7. Together with all the things said above, relax. Stay fresh with other activities. Get your sleep eat well, play a sport and don't get into unnecessary discussions about GAMSAT with people around you. You do not want any de-motivating opinion of the test or even the preparation crossing your mind.